{"title":"南方的溪涧","authors":["上官风华"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方的溪涧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京大学  上官风华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荆榛护着烂草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛤蚧养着蛇虫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溪涧躲着巨石避开悬崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羼弱得没有些许生机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知道北方大河的雄浑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亘古苍凉的细弯流程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕过祖父坟地的拱木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模糊了祖母上坟的小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这溪涧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日复一日，夜复一夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寂静着，冷漠着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麻木了一群群生灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"销蚀了一丝丝新意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知哪一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然响了一声霹雳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山洪夹着黄土沙石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲刷着在溪涧身上大踏步而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲兀立在自然的暴虐中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张大了嘴巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当溪涧重归死寂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们依然享饮溪涧的施舍时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲大喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我要去看北方的河！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲究竟没有能够去成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好在，儿子去成了"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}